 295:Generated_Source\PSoC5/cyfitter_cfg.c **** /*******************************************************************************
 296:Generated_Source\PSoC5/cyfitter_cfg.c **** * Function Name: SetAnalogRoutingPumps
 297:Generated_Source\PSoC5/cyfitter_cfg.c **** ********************************************************************************
 298:Generated_Source\PSoC5/cyfitter_cfg.c **** *
 299:Generated_Source\PSoC5/cyfitter_cfg.c **** * Summary:
 300:Generated_Source\PSoC5/cyfitter_cfg.c **** * Enables or disables the analog pumps feeding analog routing switches.
 301:Generated_Source\PSoC5/cyfitter_cfg.c **** * Intended to be called at startup, based on the Vdda system configuration;
 302:Generated_Source\PSoC5/cyfitter_cfg.c **** * may be called during operation when the user informs us that the Vdda voltage
